--------------------------------------------
Usage: pandahook create [args..]
--------------------------------------------
Follow any command with "help" for more information.

Create accepts the details necessary to create a bare repo on the hook-server.

You must provide a name for this remote repository.  As a bare repo, it will bear
the suffix *.git, but this is added automatically for you.

Required:
  -n  Name of remote repository.

  -s  Target hook-server address. Defaults to port 22.
